comments: The instructor was very available and extremely helpful; high quality support and instruction.

narratives.question_text: Discuss if you wish how this course fits into your overall program.
comments: Critically important in helping to advance ideas of my dissertation project.

Now that I am no longer taking regular course work, this course is a vital way to continue to interact with my fellow social ecology doctoral students and receive feedback on my work, as well as continue to discuss the ways in which social theory applies to the work of myself and others in the lab.
